of the industry by developing and implementing new ideas; leading by example; and
staying  true  to  our  founding  principles  of  service,  hard  work,  and  extra  effort  for
the betterment of the industry and the pavements we produce. I have concentrated
my  work  on  technology  and  technology  transfer  for  all  three  primary  segments  of
our mission: airports, highways and streets.
