Midwest Consulting Engineers, Inc., 1987–1988

Capstone:  Before  accepting  a  position  with  the  ACPA,  I  served  in  an  engineering
position  with  this  Chicago-based  design  and  construction  consulting-engineering
firm. During my tenure, I worked on several major design and construction projects,
while  also  providing  administrative  and  technical  support  to  colleagues,  and  intro-
ducing the company to computer spreadsheets for cost estimating and geometric de-
sign.

