For the next major surface transportation reauthorization, which
is coming up very soon, I would like to ask of each of the witnesses
what  you  all  think  are  the  key  research  priorities  for  the  Nation
for surface transportation in this next bill, especially in the context
of  reducing  life  cycle  energy  use  and  promoting  sustainability.
