Ms. RICHARDSON. Yes, thank you, Chairman Wu.
First  of  all,  a  statement  for  all  of  the  panelists  that  we  have
here.  Much  has  been  said  about  providing  additional  funding  for
research  but  I  would  like  to  respectfully  request  that  you  provide
to  the  Committee  is  specifically  how  much  do  you  think  would  be
