embodied  energy  in  the  materials  that  are  used  as  well  as  the  en-
ergy used to place the pavements, to recycle the pavements or to—
I  should  say  to  rehabilitate  the  pavements  over  many  cycles.  They
did  a  50-year  analysis.  That  was  information  that  we  had.  It  is
