Chairman WU. And they are civil.
Mr. BRUBAKER. And they are civil, with an emphasis on the civil.
The  point  you  were  asking  or  the  question  that  you  were  asking
before about data, I think it illustrates what I am about to say. We
really  have  to  have  a  better  understanding  of  the  holistic  perform-
